sentences.english: The YBAM HQ Secretariat reserves the right to make any alteration upon the General Rules.
sentences.chinese: 馬佛青總會祕書處有權在簡章上作任何的增刪。

sentences.english: The file can also be altered, augmented or deleted.
sentences.chinese: 文件能進行修改和增刪。

sentences.english: She amended the speech by making some additions and deletions.
sentences.chinese: 她對講話作了增刪修改。

sentences.english: Do not change the form randomly.
sentences.chinese: 請勿任意增刪列，更動格式。

sentences.english: Change can be achieved modifying a search of the small systems.
sentences.chinese: 一款能夠實現增刪改查的小系統。
